   `ontobricks-demo2` endpoint `ep-weathered-thunder-d14ri8i3.database.us-west-2.cloud.databricks.com`
2. Run: `make deploy`
3. Run: `make bootstrap-lakebase`
4. In app UI: Settings → Registry → Initialize

